    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838340/extras/3b3eccf9e5888e3c1ff2f4da1033a91d.webp?t=1751490257\" width=600 height=58 /></span>The rules are simple: one, whoever draws the shortest straw enters first. Two, no lights except your jar of fireflies. And three, whoever finds the complete collection of cards hidden in the house becomes the gang leader. Do you accept the challenge?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There’s only one problem: a presence roams the place, turning your search into hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be quick. Hide. Don’t make a noise. And above all...don’t get caught!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What begins as a game turns into a race for survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From Octavi Navarro (Thimbleweed Park, Photographs...) and Susanna Granell, creators of the critically acclaimed games <i>The Supper</i>, <i>The Librarian</i>, and the <i>Midnight Scenes </i>series<i>, </i> comes this weird and peculiar horror game for fans of the genre.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838340/extras/d99eef9d7cf222f564c2533961ab02fd.poster.avif?t=1751490257\" width=604 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838340/extras/d99eef9d7cf222f564c2533961ab02fd.webm?t=1751490257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838340/extras/d99eef9d7cf222f564c2533961ab02fd.mp4?t=1751490257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838340/extras/b3b884a619e214e41e875feb8663843e.webp?t=1751490257\" width=600 height=58 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive horror experience that will keep you on your toes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gorgeous combination of 3D environments and pixel art.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eerie soundtrack.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric sound effects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with dozens of objects in a house full of secrets, and discover the truth about its late inhabitants.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your only light source is a jar of fireflies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find all the cards hidden in the house before the presence gets you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck!!!</p>",
